            <scopecontent id="aspace_f832990a83339dda5184b16ad3ba849b">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Included in this series are: notes for course Beck taught elsewhere (New Haven YMCA Junior College, ca. 1940-1945), honorary and public lectures by Beck; writings by Beck and others, material on the American Institute of Electrical Engineers; various grants and consulting jobs by Beck; topics of general interest to Beck. This material, unlike Series I, primarily seems to be from the 1940s and 1950s.</p>
