         <c id="ref24" level="series">
            <did>
               <unittitle>Student Grade Books and Material Relating to Grades</unittitle>
               <unitid>Series IV</unitid>
               <unitdate unitdatetype="inclusive">Circa 1928-1970</unitdate>
            </did>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_609a030d5bc0780bafb5bebd4c6a7d7d">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series consists of approximately 90 grade books from [1928-1929]-1970. Books which have no dates in them have been kept in the same order as Professor Beck had them. There are also 11 folders of grade lists and other materials related to grades. This includes a folder describing Ph.D dissertation requirements, as well as sample syllabi.</p>
            </scopecontent>
